en-US.summary: Learn some facts about animals and plants.
examplePhrases: Alexa, ask living things to give me an animal fact

en-US.name: Living things
en-US.description:
Ask for animals or plants, and learn about their.

To start, just say:

"Alexa, ask living things to give me an animal fact"
"Alexa, ask living things to give me a plant fact"
"Alexa, ask living things to give me a fact"

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
